<body class="bg-gray-100 font-sans">

  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto p-8 bg-white rounded shadow-lg mt-10">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Roda Sequel App Template</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Hanami-like project structure with Roda, also featuring code reloading and autoloading via Zeitwerk. (Includes Tailwind CSS via CDN by default)</p>

    <ol class="list-decimal pl-6">
      <li class="mb-2">Clone this template to your machine:</li>
      <code class="bg-gray-200 p-2 rounded mb-4 block">git clone git@github.com:xJGBx/rodaSequelTemplate.git</code>

      <li class="mb-2">Modify the <code class="bg-gray-200 p-1 rounded">.env</code> file accordingly.</li>

      <li class="mb-2">Uncomment <code class="bg-gray-200 p-1 rounded">.gitignore</code>.</li>

      <li class="mb-2">Run <code class="bg-gray-200 p-2 rounded">bundle install</code>.</li>

      <li class="mb-2">Modify the model and migration files accordingly.</li>

      <li class="mb-2">Run <code class="bg-gray-200 p-2 rounded">rake db:create</code>.</li>

      <li class="mb-2">Run <code class="bg-gray-200 p-2 rounded">rake db:migrate</code>.</li>

      <li class="mb-2">Run <code class="bg-gray-200 p-2 rounded">rake --tasks</code> to find available commands.</li>

      <li class="mb-2">Modify <code class="bg-gray-200 p-1 rounded">router.rb</code> accordingly.</li>

      <li class="mb-2">Run <code class="bg-gray-200 p-2 rounded">bundle exec rackup</code> and view in the browser at <a href="http://127.0.0.1:9292" target="_blank" class="text-blue-500 underline">http://127.0.0.1:9292</a> by default.</li>
    </ol>
  </div>

</body>